Here is a minimal functional React component that displays “Hello World”:

```jsx
import React from "react";

function HelloWorld() {
  return <div>Hello World</div>;
}

export default HelloWorld;
```

If you prefer an arrow function version:

```jsx
import React from "react";

const HelloWorld = () => {
  return <div>Hello World</div>;
};

export default HelloWorld;
```
